\ Multi-line locals declarations and comments within them.
\ Exercises the input-refill path (a locals list spanning input lines)
\ and comment-skipping inside the locals scan.

\ (1) word locals split across lines, with \ and ( ) comments mixed in
: add3
  | >a >b      \ first two operands
    >c |       ( and the third )
  a b + c + ;
1 2 3 add3 . cr

\ (2) [| quotation locals split across lines
: hyp2
  [| >p
     >q |
     p p *  q q *  +
  :] ;
3 4 hyp2 execute . cr

\ (3) a comment containing a word identical to a local name must not
\ be read as a second declaration of that local
: sq
  | >n        \ n is the value to square
  |
  n n * ;
6 sq . cr
